cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about improving the performance of Neural Machine Translation (NMT) models through knowledge distillation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses techniques for data filtering and model compression, which are common topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also mentions the use of ensembles and oracles, which are common in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE), respectively, making these categories less likely but still possible.
